  "original_title": "\u0d9c\u0ddc\u0dc0\u0dd2 \u0dab\u0dba \u0d9a\u0db4\u0dcf\u0dc4\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Farm loans are waived",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Janathi Ranil Wickramasinghe said that the loans taken by farmers with less than 2 hectares will be written off. The President mentioned that the loans taken from the state banks will be suspended and the number of farmers who will benefit is 28000.",
        "The President also mentioned that the money due to the banks will be credited to the respective banks by the Treasury."
      ],
